In the same way,
the angular momentum will be conserved,

10
00:00:51,536 --> 00:00:54,580
which tells us that mvb is a constant.

11
00:00:54,580 --> 00:00:57,874
This means that dgamma/dt can be
expressed in terms of the initial

12
00:00:57,874 --> 00:01:00,741
