14
00:01:06,199 --> 00:01:08,203
This serves to express the Coulomb force,

15
00:01:08,203 --> 00:01:11,486
which is just the product of the two
charges divided by 4 pi r^2,

16
00:01:11,486 --> 00:01:15,260
times the unit vector which connects
the projectile and the target,

17
00:01:15,260 --> 00:01:18,535
